j is NA before the up/down split.\n\n## Deliverables\n\n- At least `output/deseq2_up.txt` must exist when you submit.\n- Full output set expected: deseq2_up.txt, deseq2_down.txt under `output/`.\n\nWhen the deliverables are in `output/`, call `submit_done(success=true)` with a short\nsummary of how you solved it.\n\n## Workspace (read-only summary)\n```json\n{\n  \"OBJECTIVE.md\": {\n    \"_file\": \"OBJECTIVE.md\"\n  },\n  \"input\": {\n    \"featureCounts_output.txt\": {\n      \"_file\": \"featureCounts_output.txt\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"meta.json\": {\n    \"_file\": \"meta.json\"\n  },\n  \"output\": {}\n}\n```\n\nSuccess hint: when `output/deseq2_up.txt` exists under the workspace, you may call submit_done(success=true).\n"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_rVLR0fCR5CPp67ywK2MYtYnQ", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"plan\": \"1. Load the featureCounts-style count matrix from 'input/featureCounts_output.txt'.\\n2. Remove rows starting with 'ERCC-' from the count matrix.\\n3. Prepare the DESeq2 dataset using the count data and condition labels.\\n4. Run DESeq2 to perform differential expression analysis.\\n5. Filter the results to remove rows with NA values in log2FoldChange or padj.\\n6. Identify upregulated genes with log2FoldChange >= 2 and write them to 'output/deseq2_up.txt'.\\n7. Identify downregulated genes with log2FoldChange <= -2 and write them to 'output/deseq2_down.txt'.\\n8. Verify the output files and submit the task as complete.\"}", "name": "write_plan"}}]}], "hide_old_env_states": false, "hide_old_action_content": false}, "observation": [{"role": "user", "content": "# Task `akinyi_deseq2`\n\n# Real R-task: akinyi_deseq2\n\n**Pipeline provenance:** `akinyi-onyango-rna_seq_pipeline-finish` (family: `rna`, stage: `late`, difficulty: `2`).\nThis workspace is derived from a real R script in the source workflow. The ground-truth\nreference output used for offline scoring lives outs